(148, 'body', '', 'Que frioooo! pero sigue sorprendiendonos,la cantitad de gente que viene a la carpa a adoptar. El dia de 25 de junio dimos todos estos lindisimos animalitos!!!! \r\n\r\n<r:assets:image id="284" width="260" /> <r:assets:image id="283" width="260" /> <r:assets:image id="280" width="260" /> <r:assets:image id="276" width="260" /> <r:assets:image id="275" width="260" /> <r:assets:image id="286" width="260" />  <r:assets:image id="279" width="260" /> <r:assets:image id="273" width="260" /> <r:assets:image id="274" width="260" /> <r:assets:image id="277" width="260" /> <r:assets:image id="281" width="260" /> <r:assets:image id="285" width="260" /> <r:assets:image id="270" width="260" /> <r:assets:image id="272" width="260" /> <r:assets:image id="278" width="260" /> <r:assets:image id="271" width="260" /> <r:assets:image id="282" width="260" /> Gracias por adoptar!', 75),
